OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FITV News UK Editor Paul Brand explains
OL,6,Fwhat happens when the Pope dies, and
OL,7,Fhow the next Pope will be selected
OL,8,Fwith the gathering of the College of
OL,9,FCardinals for the conclave.
OL,11,FThe centuries old process of the papal
OL,12,Fconclave - the election of a new Pope
OL,13,F- is underway following the death of
OL,14,FPope Francis.
OL,16,FThe election of a new pope is a
OL,17,Fspecial moment, the Vatican City will
OL,18,Fbe full of anticipation as crowds
OL,19,Fgather outside St Peter's Square
OL,20,Fwaiting for the signal that the
OL,21,Fmonumental decision has been made.
