OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FInside the Sistine Chapel, behind
OL,6,Fmarble walls and beneath
OL,7,FMichelangelo's frescoes, 120 cardinals
OL,8,Fwill gather in red robes to select the
OL,9,Fnext pope with a historic vote.
OL,11,FWith no phones or connection to the
OL,12,Foutside world - the cardinals are
OL,13,Fguided only by centuries of tradition
OL,14,Fand faith.
OL,16,FHere, ITV News explains how a pope is
OL,17,Felected and when the new pontiff will
OL,18,Fbe announced.
OL,20,FWhat is the conclave?
