OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FAll communications with the outside
OL,6,Fworld, including phones and the
OL,7,Finternet, are removed and the chapel
OL,8,Fis checked for recording devices.
OL,10,FThe cardinals are handed voting papers
OL,11,Fto write the name of the person they
OL,12,Fhave selected.
OL,14,FOne by one - in order of seniority -
OL,15,Fthey take it in turns to approach the
OL,16,Faltar where they leave it on a plate,
OL,17,Fpray, below the words "Eligo in Summun
OL,18,FPontificem" - Latin for "I elect as
OL,19,Fsupreme pontiff" - and then place it
OL,20,Fin an urn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
